This is a brand page for the COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. trademark by Covington Investment Advisors, Inc. 
                                in Ligonier, PA, 15658.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Covington Investment Advisors, Inc. of the COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. trademark.
                           






On Tuesday, March 30, 2010,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. by 
                        Covington Investment Advisors, Inc., Ligonier, PA  15658.
                        The USPTO has given the COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. 
                        trademark serial  number of  85002036.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
                        The correspondent listed for COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. is 
                        
                        
                                            CHRISTOPHE L. DIFALCO of 
                                            DIFALCO & FERNANDEZ, LLLP,  845 THIRD AVENUE, 6TH FLOOR NEW YORK, NY 10022
                                .
                            The COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for COVINGTON INVESTMENT ADVISORS, INC. 
                            is Advice relating to investments; Annuity services, namely, account and investment administration; Annuity services, namely, account and investment administration and the investment and distribution of annuity funds; Brokerage services for capital investments; Brokerage services in the field of securities and commodities investing; Equity capital investment; Financial and investment services, namely, management and brokerage in the fields of stocks, bonds, options, commodities, futures and other s. 
                            





