Overview


Covington Investment Advisors, Inc. is a boutique investment advisory firm that provides comprehensive wealth management services since 2003. Covington is a fee-only independent Federally Registered Investment Advisor located in Ligonier, Pennsylvania. Their advisory service encompasses investment management, retirement planning, life transition planning, estate planning, and 401K administration/asset management services.


